tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE user_activity (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    action_type VARCHAR(50),
    action_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    device_id UUID,
    session_id UUID
);

CREATE TABLE user_interactions (
    interaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID REFERENCES users(user_id),
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    interaction_details JSONB
);

CREATE TABLE user_analytics (
    analytics_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID REFERENCES users(user_id),
    page_visited VARCHAR(100),
    time_spent_seconds INT,
    event_type VARCHAR(50)
);
CREATE TABLE Users ( user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, username VARCHAR(255), email VARCHAR(255), created_at TIMESTAMP );
CREATE TABLE UserActivity ( activity_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, user_id UUID, activity_type VARCHAR(50), timestamp TIMESTAMP );
CREATE TABLE Interactions ( interaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, user_id UUID, interaction_type VARCHAR(50), timestamp TIMESTAMP, device_id UUID );
CREATE TABLE Reports ( report_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, user_id UUID, report_type VARCHAR(50), timestamp TIMESTAMP, status VARCHAR(50) );

CREATE TABLE app_usage (
  app_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  device_id VARCHAR(50),
  duration_minutes INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
